{"title":"第二章：MySQL环境搭建","uid":"de9047ec32ef513a8a645b78d181a805","slug":"第二章：MySQL环境搭建","date":"2023-01-06T12:21:00.000Z","updated":"2023-01-07T06:35:38.565Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/第二章：MySQL环境搭建.json","keywords":null,"cover":null,"content":"<h2 id=\"Mysql数据库的账号登录，Mysql演示使用-Mysql的编码设置\"><a href=\"#Mysql数据库的账号登录，Mysql演示使用-Mysql的编码设置\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Mysql数据库的账号登录，Mysql演示使用, Mysql的编码设置\"></a>Mysql数据库的账号登录，Mysql演示使用, Mysql的编码设置</h2><h3 id=\"Mysql的登录\"><a href=\"#Mysql的登录\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Mysql的登录\"></a>Mysql的登录</h3><ol>\n<li>输入登录账号和密码<pre class=\"line-numbers language-sql\" data-language=\"sql\"><code class=\"language-sql\">    mysql -uroot -p123456\n&#96;&#96;&#96;  \n2. 进入之后，查看Mysql版本\n&#96;&#96;&#96; sql\n    select version();</code></pre></li>\n<li>退出<pre class=\"line-numbers language-sql\" data-language=\"sql\"><code class=\"language-sql\">exit&#x2F;quit</code></pre></li>\n</ol>\n<hr>\n<h3 id=\"Mysql演示使用\"><a href=\"#Mysql演示使用\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Mysql演示使用\"></a>Mysql演示使用</h3><ol>\n<li><p>查看所有的数据库</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-sql\" data-language=\"sql\"><code class=\"language-sql\">show databases;</code></pre></li>\n<li><p>创建自己的数据库</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-sql\" data-language=\"sql\"><code class=\"language-sql\">create database 数据库名; \n# 不能与已经存在的数据库重名\ncreate database atguigu;</code></pre></li>\n<li><p>使用自己的数据库</p>\n <pre class=\"line-numbers language-sql\" data-language=\"sql\"><code class=\"language-sql\">use 数据库名; \nuse atguigu;</code></pre></li>\n<li><p>查看某个库的所有表格</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-sql\" data-language=\"sql\"><code class=\"language-sql\">show tables from 数据库名;</code></pre></li>\n<li><p>创建新的表格</p>\n <pre class=\"line-numbers language-sql\" data-language=\"sql\"><code class=\"language-sql\">create table 表名称(\n字段名 数据库类型,\n字段名 数据类型\n);\n\ncreate table student(\n    id int,\n    name varchar(20)\n)</code></pre>\n</li>\n<li><p>查看一个表的数据</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-sql\" data-language=\"sql\"><code class=\"language-sql\">select * from student;</code></pre></li>\n</ol>\n<p>7.添加一条记录<br>    <pre class=\"line-numbers language-sql\" data-language=\"sql\"><code class=\"language-sql\">insert into 表名称 values(值列表);\n\ninsert into student values(1, &#39;张三&#39;);\ninsert into sutdent values(2, &#39;李四&#39;);</code></pre></p>\n<ol start=\"8\">\n<li><p>查看表的创建信息</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-sql\" data-language=\"sql\"><code class=\"language-sql\">show create table 表名称\\G\n\nshow create table student\\G</code></pre></li>\n<li><p>查看数据库的创建信息</p>\n <pre class=\"line-numbers language-sql\" data-language=\"sql\"><code class=\"language-sql\">show create database 数据库名\\G</code></pre></li>\n<li><p>删除表格</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-sql\" data-language=\"sql\"><code class=\"language-sql\">drop table student;</code></pre>\n</li>\n<li><p>删除数据库</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-sql\" data-language=\"sql\"><code class=\"language-sql\">drop database 数据库名；</code></pre></li>\n</ol>\n<h3 id=\"Mysql的编码设置\"><a href=\"#Mysql的编码设置\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Mysql的编码设置\"></a>Mysql的编码设置</h3>","text":"Mysql数据库的账号登录，Mysql演示使用, Mysql的编码设置Mysql的登录 输入登录账号和密码 mysql -uroot -p123456 &#96;&#96;&#96; 2. 进入之后，查看Mysql版本 &#96;&#96;&#96; sql select ver...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":791,"symbolsTime":"1 mins."},"categories":[],"tags":[{"name":"数据库","slug":"数据库","count":1,"path":"api/tags/数据库.json"}],"toc":"<ol class=\"toc\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#Mysql%E6%95%B0%E6%8D%AE%E5%BA%93%E7%9A%84%E8%B4%A6%E5%8F%B7%E7%99%BB%E5%BD%95%EF%BC%8CMysql%E6%BC%94%E7%A4%BA%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8-Mysql%E7%9A%84%E7%BC%96%E7%A0%81%E8%AE%BE%E7%BD%AE\"><span class=\"toc-text\">Mysql数据库的账号登录，Mysql演示使用, Mysql的编码设置</span></a><ol class=\"toc-child\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#Mysql%E7%9A%84%E7%99%BB%E5%BD%95\"><span class=\"toc-text\">Mysql的登录</span></a></li><li clas